window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Vampire Sorcerer is the newest series from the fantasy LitRPG Hades Online world.</b></p> <p><b>Monster girls, vampire sorcerers, and dungeon cores to discover!</b></p> <p>Athanasios is forced to work in a glorified arcade, until one day, he receives an invitation in his mailbox to try a new game. But it's not the exciting new adventure he was expecting. He is tricked, and transferred to a world where goblins plague villages, dragons tear down cities, and adventurers try to loot dungeons.</p> <p>Trying to find a way out, he is turned into a vampire sorcerer. Condemned to a lifetime of trouble, Athanasios is dragged into a war with vampire slayers, ghoul-infested dungeons, and wizards from all over the continent. Fortunately, he attracts the company of a bloodthirsty vampiress, a seductive rag doll, and a nerdy wizard girl to help him in his quest.</p> <p>Join the adventure, as Athanasios goes from being little more than a pet to overpowered on his journey to become the ultimate vampire sorcerer.</p> <p><i>This series contains adult situations featuring monster girls, graphic violence, mind-blowing scenes, a lustful vampire, and sizzling hot wizards. </i></p>"; 
